Anjuro Kata

00:13:06.930 --> 00:13:07.970
Anjuro Katagiri

00:13:11.180 --> 00:13:16.420
The funeral has ended,
and his uniform hangs in the closet.

00:13:17.190 --> 00:13:24.130
And behind it, the shoes, socks, shirts, 
and pants of a middle-aged man,

00:13:24.130 --> 00:13:29.670
who would say, "What? This is what I like,"
are neatly folded and lined up.

00:13:30.480 --> 00:13:34.120
But eventually, they will 
probably be disposed of.

00:13:36.090 --> 00:13:37.810
Because, despite his daughter

00:13:37.810 --> 00:13:41.300
not wanting to throw them away 
since they hold such dear memories,

00:13:41.300 --> 00:13:44.440
no one will ever wear them again.

00:13:47.830 --> 00:13:52.050
Josuke probably doesn't 
want to see anyone right now.

00:14:04.480 --> 00:14:07.220
Everything but canned drinks
and foods is dangerous,

00:14:07.220 --> 00:14:08.740
so don't consume anything else.

00:14:10.750 --> 00:14:12.240
How's your mom?

00:14:12.240 --> 00:14:15.440
I had her go to a relative's 
house after the funeral.

00:14:15.440 --> 00:14:18.710
Good idea. She can come back 
after we kick Angelo's ass.

00:14:20.780 --> 00:14:23.360
I'm not pissed off or anything.

00:14:23.360 --> 00:14:26.300
I just got a little worked up for a moment.

00:14:26.790 --> 00:14:29.230
I'm calm. Completely calm.

00:14:29.830 --> 00:14:31.300
Calm, huh?

00:14:32.880 --> 00:14:35.370
Well, this is your furniture,

00:14:35.370 --> 00:14:38.080
so it's up to you if you want
to take out your anger on it.

00:14:38.860 --> 00:14:41.560
By the way, that scar on your lip...

00:14:42.390 --> 00:14:44.980
That's from when I punched you.

00:14:45.610 --> 00:14:48.700
Can't your Stand heal your wounds?

00:14:48.700 --> 00:14:51.730
My Stand can't heal my own wounds.

00:14:52.130 --> 00:14:57.440
What if his Stand enters your body and 
starts tearing things up from the inside?

00:14:57.440 --> 00:14:58.620
I'd probably die.

00:14:59.770 --> 00:15:02.500
If it invades me, I lose.

00:15:06.340 --> 00:15:10.090
You're gonna try to trap my 
Stand in a bottle again?

00:15:12.250 --> 00:15:17.550
That ain't happening again, Josuke. 
I know your powers very well now.

00:15:19.840 --> 00:15:21.980
Tomorrow, or the day after tomorrow...

00:15:21.980 --> 00:15:25.280
I'll wait patiently for my chance.

00:15:27.380 --> 00:15:30.450
— 3 Days Later —

00:15:32.430 --> 00:15:35.460
He's come this close to see what's going on...

00:15:35.460 --> 00:15:38.250
But these past three days,
he hasn't made a single move.

00:15:39.380 --> 00:15:42.000
What's he waiting for?

00:15:52.010 --> 00:15:53.030
It's raining...

00:15:56.650 --> 00:15:58.170
Rain?

00:16:06.020 --> 00:16:07.410
What the hell?

00:16:07.410 --> 00:16:09.260
I thought something seemed odd about you.

00:16:09.260 --> 00:16:10.890
So you're a Stand user, too?

00:16:12.260 --> 00:16:15.580
Well, whatever. I've been 
waiting for this moment.

00:16:15.580 --> 00:16:17.430
This house is now mine!

00:16:17.820 --> 00:16:20.450
You guys can't leave while it's raining!

00:16:27.950 --> 00:16:28.800
Josuke!

00:16:32.910 --> 00:16:35.570
He was just here all of a sudden, 
boiling the water.

00:16:35.570 --> 00:16:37.640
He's twisted the faucet, too.

00:16:37.640 --> 00:16:40.270
Angelo's Stand has entered the house.

00:16:40.630 --> 00:16:43.460
He wasn't waiting for you to drink the water.

00:16:44.190 --> 00:16:45.810
He was waiting for it to rain!

00:16:46.350 --> 00:16:49.400
His Stand can move in the rain... No.

00:16:49.400 --> 00:16:51.690
It can move freely in liquids.

00:16:55.710 --> 00:16:57.870
Josuke! Stay away from that kettle!

00:16:59.170 --> 00:17:00.620
The steam is him!

00:17:08.960 --> 00:17:10.940
This is just great.

00:17:10.940 --> 00:17:13.130
We can't capture him in the bottle.

00:17:13.130 --> 00:17:15.880
Stay away from the steam.
If you inhale that, you're in trouble.

00:17:15.880 --> 00:17:17.390
Get out of the kitchen.

00:17:17.390 --> 00:17:22.310
About that... It seems like it won't even 
do any good to get out of here.

00:17:23.880 --> 00:17:29.030
Angelo has already made 
several holes in the roof.

00:17:29.030 --> 00:17:32.400
So it's dangerous to go upstairs,
obviously, or outside.

00:17:32.960 --> 00:17:35.480
This is just great...

00:17:48.830 --> 00:17:51.030
I never would have thought a power

00:17:51.030 --> 00:17:54.970
that uses water could be this terrifying.

00:17:56.220 --> 00:17:58.230
He's pretty smart.

00:18:02.640 --> 00:18:05.350
What's so funny? We're trapped.

00:18:07.240 --> 00:18:08.180
Hey!

00:18:08.660 --> 00:18:10.850
I mean, Jotaro...

00:18:10.850 --> 00:18:14.850
The guy who killed my Gramps is this close.

00:18:16.210 --> 00:18:19.110
This is just great!

00:18:22.920 --> 00:18:25.620
Now, then. Let's finish this.

00:18:39.630 --> 00:18:41.140
Now, Josuke...

00:18:41.140 --> 00:18:42.950
How would you

00:18:44.090 --> 00:18:45.610
slip out of this situation?

00:18:45.610 --> 00:18:47.270
Slip out?

00:18:48.410 --> 00:18:51.610
I wouldn't quite word it like that.

00:18:56.140 --> 00:18:58.190
I would break out!

00:18:58.680 --> 00:18:59.700
Hurry, this way!

00:19:00.040 --> 00:19:01.760
The wall's going to go back to normal.

00:19:02.100 --> 00:19:03.450
Good grief.

00:19:06.500 --> 00:19:08.250
Well, we've blocked the steam...

00:19:10.840 --> 00:19:11.920
The humidifier!

00:19:13.620 --> 00:19:14.420
Josuke!

00:19:14.420 --> 00:19:17.230
I've won! Just as I thought, Josuke!

00:19:17.230 --> 00:19:20.360
I knew you'd break through the 
wall and come into this room!

00:19:21.100 --> 00:19:22.160
Shit!

00:19:24.170 --> 00:19:30.050
When horse races or test answers 
end up exactly as I expect,

00:19:30.050 --> 00:19:35.880
I can't help but feel lucky from the 
bottom of my heart and laugh.

00:19:35.880 --> 00:19:37.650
It just bubbles out!

00:19:41.200 --> 00:19:42.160
Josuke!

00:19:43.270 --> 00:19:46.910
What Angelo just said is wrong, Jotaro.

00:19:48.160 --> 00:19:49.150
Josuke?

00:19:49.150 --> 00:19:55.600
Even when things end up exactly as I expect,
I don't feel like laughing...

00:19:56.300 --> 00:19:59.090
Not when it comes to Angelo.

00:20:03.420 --> 00:20:04.400
That's...

00:20:04.950 --> 00:20:09.140
Got it. Sorry, it's a bit gross.

00:20:09.140 --> 00:20:12.560
I shredded up a rubber glove
and swallowed it beforehand.

00:20:17.450 --> 00:20:19.920
I see. It appears the user's body is over there.

00:20:23.220 --> 00:20:24.830
Sh-Shit!

00:20:29.850 --> 00:20:31.050
So you're...

00:20:31.470 --> 00:20:32.500
...Angelo.

00:20:32.500 --> 00:20:35.080
Damn it!

00:20:41.650 --> 00:20:45.970
Y-You guys aren't going to kill me, are you?!

00:20:46.520 --> 00:20:50.010
Sure, I'm an escaped death row inmate.

00:20:50.010 --> 00:20:53.480
But just because I was found
guilty by Japanese law

00:20:53.480 --> 00:20:56.150
doesn't mean you guys have 
the right to judge me!

00:20:56.150 --> 00:21:03.400
Josuke! I killed your grandpa,
but you have no right to kill me!

00:21:03.400 --> 00:21:08.140
If you kill me, you'll end up 
a cursed soul, just like me!

00:21:12.070 --> 00:21:15.580
Don't go telling people what 
they can and can't do.

00:21:16.650 --> 00:21:20.590
M-M-My right hand! My hand!

00:21:20.990 --> 00:21:23.860
No one's going to execute you.

00:21:23.860 --> 00:21:26.090
Not me, and not Jotaro, either.

00:21:26.830 --> 00:21:29.220
You're not going to be executed,

00:21:29.220 --> 00:21:31.470
and you're not going back to jail.

00:21:31.470 --> 00:21:33.600
Josuke, I'll leave the rest to you.

00:21:33.600 --> 00:21:37.100
Wh-What do you plan to do 
with me, you bastards?!

00:21:37.410 --> 00:21:39.870
Repent for eternity, Angelo!

00:21:39.870 --> 00:21:43.960
For all of those you killed, 
including my Gramps!

00:21:54.390 --> 00:21:59.250
You're gonna live forever in the 
city my Gramps protected.

